# LogEchoMatrix - Log Repetition & Pattern Analyzer

LogEchoMatrix detects high-frequency log lines, keyword clusters, and alert storms.

## Features
- Repetition summary  
- Burst detection  
- CLI-friendly  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_LogEchoMatrix.git
cd 22_LogEchoMatrix
python analyze.py logs/system.log
